"     Lactation",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Enters breast milk/not recommended (AAP considers &ldquo;compatible&rdquo;; AAP 2001 update pending)",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block brc drugH1Div\" id=\"F160640\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Breast-Feeding Considerations",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Diltiazem is excreted into breastmilk in concentrations similar to those in the maternal plasma.",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
